    "body": "This PR mitigates network issues when vcpkg downloads source tarballs by caching the entire `vcpkg/downloads` directory.\r\n\r\nCloses https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/34996.\r\n\r\n**Note for Maintainers:** To properly populate the new CI cache, all current vcpkg binary caches must be cleared to trigger a rebuild.",
